{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, it was a posh street. See it was like these streets here, {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Dempsey Street{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Dempsey Street{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, all this area here was the posh part of Stepney. One of the posh - what I call 
you know - policemen lived and - and - shop - all sorts of people you know. But poor people couldn't afford to pay expensive rent.
