ters had their two rooms out the house as a - tailors workshop. One was a trousers maker, one was a coat maker and one was - they're all different trades. And they use them as workshops, the houses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7229527 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2968889\charrsid66970 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
