 - in the leather shop, they wanted someone there. So - when I went down to - there, I got a job. And then - I wasn't - there a - three or four months, and then - someone else asked me if I want another job. Used to stop and ask you. See? In the trade kne
w you. If you went in the leather shop they'd say, here I've got a job for you, a good job.
