learn a little off of you and you learn a little off of them, if you're sensible, in a trade, that's how I used to. And working with these foreigners in the East End here - from {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname 
country-region}}Russia{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} - they have got - they call made to and mend ideas, they do things what
 you never thought of. You see. There's - there's ways of doing something easy if you only know, but if you don't know so you work the hard way round.
