{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Mile End Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} or anywhere. The last horse trams I saw running - was in Burdett Road, it run from the Docks, West India Docks - up to - Stoke Newington, 
