y made a - a - a - a centre line, so there used to be a - like a - a needle went in that - centre line - it - brought the power up so the horses couldn't tread on that, but the other - the old stud system - they tod on - there was like a big stud, every t
ime the tram - touched it I suppose it threw 'em a - a distance away. But the horses treading on them studs and they got electrocuted so they had this all done away with Mm.
